      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... i don't want a different kind of landing. i just want to check out. i've been wandering around this itinerary for so long and i'm just ready to close the book. it feels like the most honest thing to do is just to stop traveling altogether and find that final, quiet spot where the path finally ends.",
